      Right.  A good way to do this would be to create national E-initiative, referendum and recall and give the voters the option of voting either online or by conventional ballot.  23 US states already have I&R and many other countries.  The US needs to catch up if it is serious about open and transparent government.  Furthermore, E-I&R would be very useful in hastening economic recovery, promoting world peace and creating a sustainable environment.  For more, please see: http://sites.google.com/site/redesignthenationonline/

                  
